     	<div id="post-103401" class="post-103401 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-sensor-sweep" >
	
<div class="loophead">
<h2 class="boxh3"><a href="http://www.castaliahouse.com/sensor-sweep-lord-dunsany-red-sonja-movie-michael-moorcock/" rel="bookmark" title="Sensor Sweep: Lord Dunsany, Red Sonja Movie, Michael Moorcock" class="tre">Sensor Sweep: Lord Dunsany, Red Sonja Movie, Michael Moorcock</a></h2>
<span class="postcalendar"><a href="http://www.castaliahouse.com/sensor-sweep-lord-dunsany-red-sonja-movie-michael-moorcock/" rel="bookmark" title="Sensor Sweep: Lord Dunsany, Red Sonja Movie, Michael Moorcock" class="tre">Monday , 18, August  2025  </a></span>
<span class="postauthor">Morgan</span>
<span class="postcategory"><a href="http://www.castaliahouse.com/category/sensor-sweep/" rel="category tag">Sensor Sweep</a></span>
